                                            <div class="_1t2xqmi">
                                                <h3
                                                    tabindex="-1"
                                                    class="hpipapi atm_7l_1kw7nm4 atm_c8_1x4eueo atm_cs_1kw7nm4 atm_g3_1kw7nm4 atm_gi_idpfg4 atm_l8_idpfg4 atm_kd_idpfg4_pfnrn2 dir dir-ltr"
                                                    elementtiming="LCP-target"
                                                >
                                                    Balian Beach, Bali, Indonesia
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div style="line-height: 1.5rem; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; display: -webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp: 3; -webkit-box-orient: vertical;">
                                                <span>
                                                    <span class="lrl13de atm_kd_19r6f69_24z95b atm_kd_19r6f69_1xbvphn_1oszvuo dir dir-ltr">
                                                        I love the feeling of a small community in this village, everyone knows each other and is super friendly. There is a nice mixture of people, local and
                                                        foreign and all kinds of ages as well. Since we are not the only one who have discovered Balian there are people in Balian creating more beautiful places to
                                                        stay. <br />
                                                        <br />
                                                        SURFING:<br />
                                                        Within 5 minute walking distance from the house you will find 3 beautiful peaks. Excellent for beginners as well as experienced surfers.<br />
                                                        <br />
                                                        At a 15 minute driving distance you will find Medewi, well known for Bali's longest ride when it lines up on a S-SW Swell<br />
                                                        All the other surf spots are at a 20 minute - 3 hour drive around the island<br />
                                                        <br />
                                                        This village is a great place to start your holiday (be careful some never left) or end your trip.
                                                    </span>
                                                </span>
