                                                                                <span class="lrl13de atm_kd_19r6f69_24z95b atm_kd_19r6f69_1xbvphn_1oszvuo dir dir-ltr">
                                                                                    This place ✨. Nestled into “jungle”. VERY private. I basically had the entire property to myself. Swimming in the pool at night
                                                                                    looking up through the banana tree palms, floating on my back under the cascade of the midnight stars. The home owners attention
                                                                                    to detail of the homes decor. From the pebbles that adorn the wall holes as art to the type of pillows used in each of the
                                                                                    “nesting” spots. This place served as a refuge for my soul. And! A super fun wave out front! <br />
                                                                                    Made is the absolute man! Very comfortable to communicate with. Gave a personalized service to my requests of rescuing me when I
                                                                                    got lost in the dark (haha! Not kidding) to driving me to a sunset view to hiring a driver for a personal tour of local rice
